# LeetCode Tracker - Local Configuration
#
# Configuration is stored in ~/.leetcode-tracker/config.json
# Run `leetcode-tracker init` to create it, then edit the file.
#
# Required: Set at least one AI provider API key
#   - Google Gemini: https://aistudio.google.com
#   - Groq: https://console.groq.com
#   - NVIDIA NIM: https://build.nvidia.com
#
# Example config.json:
# {
#   "aiProvider": "google",
#   "aiModel": "",
#   "geminiApiKey": "your-key-here",
#   "groqApiKey": "",
#   "nvidiaApiKey": "",
#   "port": 3000
# }
